&lt;p&gt;
For easy installation a spacemacs layer that also uses the
&lt;a href="https://github.com/dougm/robot-mode"&gt;robot-mode package&lt;/a&gt; by Doug MacEachern can be found &lt;a href="https://github.com/dalanicolai/robot-framework-layer"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.
